reektownDetroit.jpg|100px]]\n|1875\n|646 Monroe Street, Detroit<br/><small>{{coord|42|20|9|N|83|2|26|W|name=Old St. Mary's Roman Catholic Church}}</small>\n|Romanesque Revival\n|Peter J. Dederichs\n|Listed as a [[Michigan State Historic Preservation Office|Michigan Historic Site]].<ref name=sitesonline/>\n|-\n|[[Saints Peter and Paul Church, Detroit, Michigan|Saints Peter and Paul Church]]\n|[[File:Saints Peter and Paul Church Detroit MI.jpg|100px]]\n|1848\n|629 E. Jefferson Avenue, Detroit<br/><small>{{coord|42|19|55|N|83|2|18|W|name=Saints Peter and Paul Church}}</small>\n|Romanesque Revival\n|Francis Letouneau, Peter Kindenkins\n|Listed on the [[National Register of Historic Places]]<ref name=NationalRegisterWayne/> and as a [[Michigan State Historic Preservation Office|Michigan Historic Site]].<ref name=sitesonline/>\n|-\n|[[Saints Peter and Paul Academy]], aka St. Patrick Senior Center\n|[[File:Sts Peter and Paul Academy - Detroit Michigan.jpg|100px]]\n|1892\n|64 Parsons Street, Detroit<br/><small>{{coord|42|20|54|N|83|3|37|W|name=Saints Peter and Paul Academy, St. Patrick Senor Center}}</small>\n|Gothic Revival\n|Leon Coquard\n|Listed on the [[National Register of Historic Places]].<ref name=NationalRegisterWayne/>\n|-\n|[[St. Stanislaus Bishop and Martyr Roman Catholic Church]]\n|[[File:St Stanislaus Roman Catholic Church Detroit.jpg|100px]]\n|1900\n|5818 Dubois, Detroit<br/><small>{{coord|42|22|19|N|83|2|49|W|name=St. Stanislaus Bishop and Martyr Roman Catholic Church}}</small>\n|Late Gothic Revival, [[Beaux-Arts architecture|Beaux-Arts]], Renaissance\n|Kastler & Hunter, Harry J. Rill\n|Listed on the [[National Register of Historic Places]]<ref name=NationalRegisterWayne/> and as a [[Michigan State Historic Preservation Office|Michigan Historic Site]].<ref name=sitesonline/>\n|-\n|[[St. Theresa of Avila Roman Catholic Church]]\n|[[File:St. Theresa of Avila Church Detroit.jpg|100px]]\n|1919\n|8666 Quincy Avenue, Detroit<br/><small>{{coord|42|21|49|N|83|7|11|W